{"tid":576677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(馬來西亞) 網民一面倒反對「一夫多妻」制","createTime":"2018-03-01T05:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T06:50:55.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"38a40e010bb806f7f4eb2072515c7672f2a99c5a","tid":576677,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.orientaldaily.com.my/s/233462\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientaldaily.com.my%2Fs%2F233462&d=RGp9JNBq2JpZLziH3TcFb8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=4a70a8c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orientaldaily.com.my/s/233462</a><br />\n<br />\n最後更新 2018年03月1日 10時31分<br />\n<br />\n社團促馬華向政府爭取「一夫多妻」制<br />\n6.1k分享<br />\n<br />\n（麻坡28日訊）<strong>為挽救華裔人口日益下降，麻坡桃源俱樂部主席余仁何公開獻計，促請馬華向政府爭取允許華裔「一夫多妻」制，改善華裔人口不斷減少的窘境。</strong><br />\n<br />\n「目前華裔只佔總人口的20%，這個比例近年來仍不斷走下坡，確實令人擔憂，在多元族群國家中，少數民族的政經文教會有很大衝擊。」<br />\n<br />\n因此，他鼓勵，時下青年男女早婚及多生育，提升我國華裔人口的比例。與此同時，他希望馬華能協助向政府爭取允准華裔一夫多妻制，挽救華裔人口持續下降的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>余仁何昨晚出席該俱樂部主辦的農歷新年團拜晚會上，提出上述建議，受到出席者歡呼和報以掌聲。出席者包括該俱樂部副主席拿督鄭伙源、拿督辜金強、拿督林聲宏、劉坤福、總務劉文行、董事黃秀蘭。<br />\n<br />\n網民一面倒不贊成<br />\n<br />\n余仁何建議「一夫多妻」制引起網民熱議，大部分網民一面倒不贊成一夫多妻制，有網民認為，華人重質不重量，並考慮經濟因素，所以不會多生。</strong>"},{"pid":"5e0bea784d012fb0a505e9abf37f31d0aff3c054","tid":576677,"uid":164167,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"試下一妻多夫"},{"pid":"c832375f9a8c284b02a8a4ef149d0c6c6ba3de2e","tid":576677,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e180e657a9b0e8335e8664bfdbdf7e40e5304bf7","tid":576677,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"想知反對嘅理由"},{"pid":"6ffaa9c18d11de5a3409b89a8b286f19a359225a","tid":576677,"uid":84869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e0bea784d012fb0a505e9abf37f31d0aff3c054","tid":576677,"uid":164167,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"試下一妻多夫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:04:40.000Z","msg":"一妻多夫 對人口增加無幫助"},{"pid":"36bdbb1db25b2ac5eb49381d75b5b2b3b84e5b16","tid":576677,"uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e180e657a9b0e8335e8664bfdbdf7e40e5304bf7","tid":576677,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"想知反對嘅理由"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:05:49.000Z","msg":"「一夫多妻」 =  少部分有錢男人娶哂大部分女人"},{"pid":"fb3e5f6cc8450a0b5e22d1b73cb5050818f81798","tid":576677,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:06:15.000Z","msg":"一個已經夠煩，重多妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0ec809b704ea445e8726473ba91cdc664f405f","tid":576677,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ffaa9c18d11de5a3409b89a8b286f19a359225a","tid":576677,"uid":84869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e0bea784d012fb0a505e9abf37f31d0aff3c054","tid":576677,"uid":164167,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"試下一妻多夫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:04:40.000Z","msg":"一妻多夫 對人口增加無幫助"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:10:37.000Z","msg":"強姦非刑事化應該有用過一夫多妻"},{"pid":"6d5a16f346086cbb7072193608f80dba13f8fe39","tid":576677,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:11:25.000Z","msg":"想增加家暴個案<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715d804d56294f9dbb57e40d653ffcc4e86763ff","tid":576677,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:18:26.000Z","msg":"幾十年後爭產案數字直線上升"},{"pid":"cd033deb84e64e0f177825f77833e9fac17f3cb7","tid":576677,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:50:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}